Jobs.job_description: We are a dynamic Moroccan startup at the forefront of technology innovation cutting-edge application with a focus on delivering exceptional user experiences. Our project encompasses a sophisticated front-end built on Next.js/React.js, a secure and robust Identity and Access Management (IAM) via Keycloak, and backend microservices architected in Java using the Quarkus framework. We are on a mission to revolutionize our industry and are looking for a passionate Backend Developer to join our team and contribute to the development of high-quality backend services.
